casebody.data:
Patti STEVENS-RUCKER, Administrator of the Estate of Jason White, Deceased, petitioner,
v.
John FRENZ, et al. No. 18-684. Supreme Court of the United States March 4, 2019.

Motion of The Rutherford Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
